---
title: Bulgur-Stuffed Peppers with Fresh Mozzarella and Sweet Onion Salad
description: Biber dolmasi are Turkish stuffed and roasted peppers. In this recipe, we have created a HelloFresh spin on this traditional dish by stuffing peppers with bulgur wheat and sun-dried tomatoes, to give a delicious smoky flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bulgur-stuffed-peppers-0aef4b54.jpg
